{"word":"οἴκαδε","slug":"οἴκαδε","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>οἴκαδε</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:οἶκόνδε'><el>οἶκόνδε</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to one's home, home, homewards</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>= <a href='S:οἴκοι'><el>οἴκοι</el></a>, <i>at home</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b> <el>οἴκαδις</el>, Doric for <el>οἴκαδε</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}